c: 13
v: 30
t: "Thus have We sent you (O Prophet!) within a people before whom (other) peoples have (gone and) passed away; So that you may repeat to them what We send down to you by inspiration; Yet they reject (Him), the Most Gracious (Ar-Rahman)! Say: \"He is my Lord! There is no god but He, my trust is upon Him and (only) to Him I turn"